        <mxCell id="webhook-receiver" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#e1d5e7;strokeColor=#9673a6;fontSize=10;align=left;spacingLeft=10;" value="Webhook Receiver (Fastify)&#xa;━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━&#xa;• Separate service (independent scaling)&#xa;• X-Hub-Signature-256 verification&#xa;• Immediate 200 OK response (&lt;5s SLA)&#xa;• Deduplication via Redis SETNX&#xa;• Enqueue to BullMQ for async processing&#xa;• Handles: messages, status updates, errors" vertex="1">
